nodes.text: The Exterminator was a Star Destroyer being manufactured in 3 ABY for the Imperial Navy by Kuat Drive Yards. As the Exterminator's construction neared its finish, the amateur slicer Shannon Voorson managed to slice into an Imperial computer file listing a number of Star Destroyers being built at Kuat, including Exterminator. Shannon later showed the Star Destroyer list to her cousin and Rebel Alliance member, Deen Voorson.
